# üéØ 1) ‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á Backend (‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô)

‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô API ‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏∞‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ:

```
Route  ‚Üí  Controller  ‚Üí  Service  ‚Üí  Repository  ‚Üí  Database
```

‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏≠‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏¢‡πå‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ô INT161 ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏à‡∏£‡∏¥‡∏á

---

# üéØ 2) ‡∏Ñ‡∏ß‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏´‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏Ç‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÅ‡∏ï‡πà‡∏•‡∏∞‡∏ä‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô (‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏Ñ‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å)

## ‚úî Route

‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏ß‡πà‡∏≤ URL ‡πÑ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£

```js
router.post("/", controller.createStudent);
router.get("/:id", controller.getStudentById);
```

---

## ‚úî Controller

‡∏£‡∏±‡∏ö request ‚Üí ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ service ‚Üí ‡∏™‡πà‡∏á response

```js
async createStudent(req, res) {
  try {
    const data = await service.createStudent(req.db, req.body);
    res.status(201).json(data);
  } catch (err) {
    res.status(err.status ?? 500).json({ error: err.message });
  }
}
```

---

## ‚úî Service

‡∏°‡∏µ logic ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô validation

```js
if (!body.fullname) throw { status: 400, message: "fullname required" };
```

---

## ‚úî Repository

‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ê‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏ú‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô Prisma ORM

```js
db.student.create({ data });
```

---

# üéØ 3) ‡∏™‡∏¥‡πà‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô backend JS

## ‚úî 1) ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á export / import ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô

export:

```js
module.exports = {...}
```

import:

```js
const service = require("../services/studentService");
```

---

## ‚úî 2) ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ async/await (‡∏™‡∏≥‡∏Ñ‡∏±‡∏ç‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏Å)

‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô async ‡∏Å‡πà‡∏≠‡∏ô function
‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ await ‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤ code ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏ï‡πà‡∏≠ DB

```js
async function test() {
  const data = await db.student.findMany();
}
```

---

## ‚úî 3) ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ try/catch ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ error

```js
try {
  ...
} catch (err) {
  res.status(500).json({ error: err.message });
}
```

‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏ä‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏≠‡∏≠‡∏Å error handling

---

## ‚úî 4) ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏≠‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô req.body ‡πÅ‡∏•‡∏∞ req.params

```js
req.body        // JSON ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å client (POST/PUT)
req.params.id   // ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏£‡πÉ‡∏ô URL ‡πÄ‡∏ä‡πà‡∏ô /students/5
```

---

# üéØ 4) ‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î backend ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà ‚Äú‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î‚Äù (‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ)

‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡πâ‡∏î‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà **‡∏à‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡πÇ‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏á‡∏™‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡∏Å‡πá‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏î‡πâ‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß**

---

# ‚úî Route (routes/studentRoutes.js)

```js
const express = require("express");
const router = express.Router();
const controller = require("../controllers/studentController");

router.post("/", controller.createStudent);
router.get("/:id", controller.getStudentById);
router.put("/:id", controller.updateStudent);
router.delete("/:id", controller.deleteStudent);

module.exports = router;
```

---

# ‚úî Controller (controllers/studentController.js)

```js
const service = require("../services/studentService");

module.exports = {
  async createStudent(req, res) {
    try {
      const data = await service.createStudent(req.db, req.body);
      res.status(201).json(data);
    } catch (err) {
      res.status(err.status ?? 500).json({ error: err.message });
    }
  }
};
```

---

# ‚úî Service (services/studentService.js)

```js
module.exports = {
  async createStudent(db, body) {
    if (!body.fullname) 
      throw { status: 400, message: "fullname required" };

    return await db.student.create({
      data: {
        fullname: body.fullname,
        age: body.age,
        email: body.email
      }
    });
  }
};
```

---

# ‚úî Repository (repositories/studentRepository.js)

```js
module.exports = {
  async createStudent(db, data) {
    return await db.student.create({ data });
  }
};
```

---

# üéØ 5) ‡∏Å‡∏é‡∏à‡∏≥‡∏á‡πà‡∏≤‡∏¢ ‡πÜ ‡πÄ‡∏ß‡∏•‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ô JS backend

## ‚úî ‡∏Å‡∏é‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏Ç 3

‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏≠‡∏∞‡πÑ‡∏£‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ï‡∏≤‡∏° ‚Äú‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏¢‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ö‡∏ê‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‚Äù ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÉ‡∏™‡πà

1. async
2. await
3. try/catch

---

## ‚úî ‡∏Å‡∏é 400 / 404 / 500

* ‡πÇ‡∏à‡∏ó‡∏¢‡πå validation ‚Üí 400
* ‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏û‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏• ‚Üí 404
* ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏°‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏ß‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏£‡∏π‡πâ‡∏™‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏´‡∏ï‡∏∏ ‚Üí 500

---

## ‚úî ‡∏Å‡∏é‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏™‡πà‡∏á error ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö

‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡πÇ‡∏¢‡∏ô‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏ó‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ô‡∏±‡πâ‡∏ô

```js
throw { status: 400, message: "fullname required" };
```

---

# ‚ù§Ô∏è ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏Ñ‡∏∏‡∏ì‡πÄ‡∏£‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å 0 ‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏ó‡∏≥‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö‡∏ô‡∏µ‡πâ

‡∏â‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ï‡∏±‡πâ‡∏á step ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ:

